          <h5 style="text-align: center;">COMPUTER VISION</h5>
          <p class="m-1 mb-3">Navigation is a crucial aspect of any autonomous technology in the field, whether it is land management or harvesting. We are in the process of developing computer vision software capable of identifying coffee and other integral parts of the landscape (tree branches, leaves, tree trunks, etc). This would enable autonomous harvesters and autonomous land management robots to not only locate coffee cherries, but also find their way around the coffee farm.</p>
          <img class="w-100 border" src="/img/contentimgs/coffee_computervision.jpg">
        </div>
        <div class="projsection text-center">
          <svg id="harvester" class="mx-auto d-block my-5" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="#319966" class="bi bi-diamond-half" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
