          <h5 style="text-align: center;">ROBOTIC LAND MANAGEMENT</h5>
          <p class="m-1 mb-3">As part of our eventual goal of a harvester, we plan to start work on a land management robot. Using a previously commissioned chassis, we plan to prototype and field test an autonomous land management robot. We plan to develop this as a field robot which uses the coffee trees as landmarks in order to navigate the field. This will keep coffee clear of invasive weeds such as kudzu, while also preparing a potential chassis for a harvester.</p>
